If diversification_check.diversification_pass is false, escalate in the note and hold all allocation changes until the Asset Selector cron provides more assets.
The shortfall field should equal target_daily_usd - current_daily_avg_usd. If shortfall > 800, flag capital rotation or new asset addition as the bottleneck.
The bottleneck field must identify the single most constraining factor preventing \$1K/day throughput."
